What is Balayage?
Balayage is a French word meaning "to sweep" or "to paint." It is a hair coloring technique that creates a natural, sun-kissed effect. Unlike traditional highlights, balayage involves hand-painting color onto the hair, resulting in a more blended and seamless look. This technique is ideal for those seeking a low-maintenance yet stylish option, as it grows out beautifully and requires less frequent touch-ups. For those looking for thebest balayage in Dubai, Code Hair is the ultimate destination.

